            "body": "Hi @tricktux ,  following up on this I have opened a PR with an implementation that addresses this enhancement. \nI added `vim.secure.source(path)` as an additive wrapper over `vim.secure.read()` to handle the compilation and execution of the configuration strings automatically, along with proper chunk naming and test coverage.\n",
